<define-tag pagetitle>License information</define-tag>
#use wml::debian::template title="<pagetitle>" GEN_TIME="yes"
#use wml::debian::recent_list

<p>These site presents the opinion of the Debian project on how
certain licenses meet the standards set by the
<a href="$(HOME)/social_contract#guidelines">Debian Free Software
Guidelines</a> (DFSG). Most of these opinions were formed in
discussions on the <a href="http://lists.debian.org/debian-legal/">\
debian-legal mailing list</a>. If you have questions or comments
about one of these license summaries, please contact the list.</p>

<p>There are three different lists of licenses available:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><a href="bydate">chronological ordered list</a>, sorted
            after the date of the summary.</li>
          <li><a href="byname">alphabetical ordered list</a>, sorted
            by the name of the license.</li>
          <li><a href="byclass">list ordered after classification</a>,
            alphabetical lists of the licenses, divided in
            <a href="byclass#free">free</a> licenses,
            <a href="byclass#non-free">non-free</a> licenses, and
            licenses that <a href="byclass#non-dist">don't allow
              redistribution</a>.</li>
        </ul>

<h2>Most recent summaries</h2>

<:= get_recent_list( '.', '10', '$(ENGLISHDIR)/legal/licenses', 'list', 'dls-.*' ) :>

